org.sdm.spa

Class SoaplabServiceClient

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.sdm.spa.SoaplabServiceClient

  • public class SoaplabServiceClient
extends java.lang.Object
    The following client is used by other web service soaplab related actors while executing the web service as well as transmitting the above client through various actors in the workflow. The gist of the following client lies in the doCall method which establishes contact with the WSDL and executes the desired enetered operation.
    Author:
    Nandita Mangal
    Category.name:
    web, external execution
